---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Andrew Giffen"
  description="Product leader in Toronto. I build B2B SaaS in complex domains-AI, integrations, and platforms that teams can actually ship."
>
  <section class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="page-label">About</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Hey, I'm Andrew.</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <p class="intro-text">
          I‚Äôm a Toronto-based product leader who likes hard problems: messy workflows, high-stakes domains,
